entries.arrived_at_delivery: We see you have arrived at the transfer location, pilot. Wait for shuttle arrival.
entries.docking_complete_delivery: Ok, we have the data. We have a message for you from your superior on Yavin 4. You are to return to base and report in. Be safe out there, pilot.
entries.docking_started_delivery: We are beginning data transfer now. Please stand by.
entries.failed_destroyed: You allowed your transfer shuttle to be destroyed? That was an expensive ship. You are going to have to answer to your commander about this failure.
entries.found_loc_d: Proceed to the following coordinates for data transfer.
entries.hello_d: Greetings, pilot. I understand that you have something for us.
entries.quest_dock2_d: Once the shuttle arrives, target it and press the 'U' key to transfer the data to the shuttle.
entries.quest_location_d: Remain in the Endor system and travel to the supplied navigation waypoint to the arrival location of the command shuttle.
entries.quest_rendezvous2_d: Travel to the navigaiton waypoint and wait for the arrival of the Command Shuttle.
entries.title: Endor System: Deliver Encrypted Rebel Data to Command Shuttle
entries.title_d: Remain in the Endor system and deliver the encrypted Rebel data to a command shuttle. You will receive a navigation waypoint to arrival location of the command shuttle. Travel to that location and wait for the shuttle to arrive. Once it arrives, target the shuttle and press the 'U' key to transfer the data to it.
